  <CalDefinition Description="To minimize the message load on the MOST network in case the RSE is active on the CenterStackDisplay  this parameter gives the time in which touch events are buffered before they will be sent to the RSE-System. The proximity event or the first touch event (start of a gesture) are sent immediately. A release event will trigger the sending of the events buffered so far even if the time for buffering has not ended." Name="CSHMI_AUX_TOUCH_EVENT_BUFFER_TIME" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,GLOBALB">
