  <CalDefinition Description="This defines how quickly the volume should increase or decrease as the user presses and holds their finger. This calibration defines how many milliseconds should pass in between increasing or decreasing the volume by one step while the finger is held. " Name="VOLUME_PRESS_HOLD_VOLUMESLEWRATE" References="GIS-500" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
