    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>2</Version>
      <Date>6/12/2015</Date>
      <Description>Updated resolution for the VOLUME_PRESS_HOLD_VOLUMESLEWRATE CAL from 10 to 1 to be able to set this CAL to the same value used for current production that is yielding optimized performance for faceplate volumn adjustements.</Description>
